{"tid":2501250,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港台：外交部重申所謂新疆存在種族滅絕是國際反華勢力大謊言","createTime":"2021-04-23T08:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T09:11:29.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd09ebd8156cdc6828a37c8a28cd12115434411","tid":2501250,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅重申，所謂中國新疆存在種族滅絕，是國際反華勢力炮製的彌天大謊。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅在記者會上，回應有關英國國會下議院通過動議，認為維吾爾族和其他少數民族，正遭受反人類罪及種族滅絕的事件。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅指出，中國政府及新疆各族人民，堅決反對並強烈譴責所謂的新疆種族滅絕，又指英國自身問題都夠多，建議有關議員，多管自己的事情，為自己的選民做多一點實事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587372-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587372-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=90642880\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587372-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=618851cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587372-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"96932674cb1c752a8428f6a77503e713ace3de5d","tid":2501250,"uid":241648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"咁算唔算干預人哋內政"},{"pid":"9dc99d34ea491fa10dc333e1f284c55ee9c21b70","tid":2501250,"uid":221343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:44:00.000Z","msg":"有晒人證物證都叫彌天大謊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠唔夠膽擺上國際審訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26725eeece7d220941c296f3d5683f7adecb1598","tid":2501250,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcim69jpRJFTAw2FAHaoi4cMqkGJX1LwKHCK1ajC5DuJ3?filename=63kuubs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th